re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T19:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾唐僧取左西經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錯"},{"pid":"ae8b63e6ef52faa161338f01370e61b18b7d0e36","tid":122111,"uid":5980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T21:25:17.000Z","msg":"比人中出左咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b21123d86908f7b0d9e78b09dd6501a056e387","tid":122111,"uid":29099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T22:09:05.000Z","msg":"西京唔係開封咩"},{"pid":"b63eb1be7bbe05aa9642391f12a96ba9ceff82ca","tid":122111,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"為了取西京每步哪敢放鬆"},{"pid":"d09cf7a5c354311985c5c6ae972cde8979a02fbd","tid":122111,"uid":56847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為了取西京每步哪敢放鬆</blockquote><br />\n為了取西經你共我極衝動"},{"pid":"1eebe3ce1018d3eccbd78577243f6a83e79d3dc2","tid":122111,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西京唔係開封咩</blockquote><br />\n開封係東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16ae3064996ffc81e2b5ccdba22753dc9ec6415","tid":122111,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西京唔係開封咩</blockquote><br />\n開封係東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洛陽先係宋西京"},{"pid":"713d2f1225dfc6552821db8a477931e500bfe0d2","tid":122111,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"西周的宗周鎬京，在今陝西省西安市。<br />\n<br />\n西漢別稱西京。<br />\n<br />\n東漢的陪都西京長安，在今陝西省西安市。<br />\n<br />\n曹魏黃初二年（221年），長安列為五都之一。（即西都，見《魏志&middot;文帝紀》引《魏略》）<br />\n<br />\n武周光宅元年（684年），武后遷都洛陽，稱為「神都」東京，而長安成為陪都西京。唐中宗神龍二年（706年）還都長安。<br />\n<br />\n唐肅宗至德二年（757年），改京兆府長安為中京[1]，改鳳翔為西京鳳翔府，在今陝西省寶雞市鳳翔縣。<br />\n<br />\n唐代渤海國的西京鴨綠府，在今吉林白山市臨江，一說在朝鮮半島慈江道鴨綠江東岸。<br />\n<br />\n北宋陪都西京河南府，在今河南省洛陽市。<br />\n<br />\n西夏陪都西京西平府，在今寧夏靈武市。<br />\n<br />\n遼代陪都西京大同府，在今山西省大同市。<br />\n<br />\n金代陪都西京大同府，在今山西省大同市。<br />\n<br />\n元代陪都西京大同府，在今山西省大同市。<br />\n<br />\n中華民國國民政府原鼎金陵，擬於今陝西省西安市建陪都，曾更名西京市。"},{"pid":"7af1c2ae7e53f1b38ebd015b7e978f352f1d483f","tid":122111,"uid":43449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比人中出左咪無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母"}]}